y (tawakkul) and seeking truth (ilm). I share that taking a vaccine is a form of stewardship for one’s health, echoing the idea that we are caretakers of our bodies, a concept echoed in both my religious teachings and my daily routine of baking and hiking, where preparation and care are paramount.

